      "title": "A position for Ranjan before coming out",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Manusha Nanayakkara, Minister of Labor and Foreign Employment, said that Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake, who will be released, will be given the new position.",
        "Mr. Nanayakkara also said that the position will be announced this evening."
